        <p class="signals-section__description">
          These signals alert you to shifts in the rapidly changing crupto markets so you’ll be the first to know and prepared to act when the market moves.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 signals-section__col signals-section__col--vertical-center">
