            buyDescription: "When an abnormally high amount of ETH move out of exchanges and into cold storage wallets, it likely indicates that the holders don’t plan to sell soon. CoinFi monitors exchange wallets.",
            sellDescription: "When an abnormally high amount of BTC/ETH moves into exchanges, it likely indicates that holders are looking to sell.",
          } %>

